    "descrizione_en": "While wearing this armor, you have a swimming speed equal to\nyour walking speed. In addition, whenever you start your turn\nunderwater with 0 hit points, the armor causes you to rise 60 feet\ntoward the surface. The armor is decorated with fish and shell\nmotifs.\nDungeon Master's Guide (BR)",
