    "descrizione_en": "While wearing this armor, you gain a +1 bonus to AC. You can also\nuse a bonus action to speak the armor's command word and cause\nthe armor to assume the appearance of a normal set of clothing or\nsome other kind of armor. You decide what it looks like, including\ncolor, style, and accessories, but the armor retains its normal bulk\nand weight. The illusory appearance lasts until you use this\nproperty again or remove the armor.\nDungeon Master's Guide (SRD)",
