    "descrizione_en": "While you wear this cloak with its hood up, Wisdom (Perception)\nchecks made to see you have disadvantage, and you have advantage\non Dexterity (Stealth) checks made to hide, as the cloak's color\nshifts to camouflage you. Pulling the hood up or down requires an\naction.\nDungeon Master's Guide (SRD)",
