    "descrizione_en": "While this pearl is on your person, you can use an action to speak\nits command word and regain one expended spell slot. If the\nexpended slot was of 4th level or higher, the new slot is 3rd level.\nOnce you have used the pearl, it can't be used again until the next\ndawn.\nDungeon Master's Guide (SRD)",
